title: Speck CandyShell Clear iPhone 6 & 6S Case 73684-5085 - Overview
description:
Speck CandyShell Clear iPhone 6 & 6S Case  - 73684-5085 http://www.abt.com/product/94981/Speck-736845085.html

Patented design provides two layers of protection. This CandyShell Clear iPhone 6s / iPhone 6 case is certified to meet or exceed MIL-STD-810G drop test standards.
Features:
• Military-grade drop protection
• Patented one-piece multi-layer design
• Patented raised bezel screen protection
• Precision-engineered slim fit
• Perimeter port and camera protection
• Lab-tested durability
• Responsive button protection
